{"tid":2360573,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（冷知識）上午10時05分是公司最常解僱員工的時間","createTime":"2021-01-10T02:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T03:02:48.000Z","uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"736bca664c670abf85a92ac2adb447f4e8b57e1f","tid":2360573,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T02:05:29.000Z","msg":"近日武漢肺炎疫情持續，很多公司為節流而宣布解僱員工。據非正式統計，如被解僱的員工，通常會在上午10時05分得知消息。<br />\n<br />\n為甚麼公司一般在上午10時05分解僱員工呢？因為上班時間通常在上午9時或之前，10時左右大部分員工已在公司。公司高層一般不是即日決定解僱員工，由於高層或老闆通常會稍晚一點回到公司，他們上班時隨即會把解僱信傳至人事部，此時已是10時左右。人事部員工一般會再用5分鐘把解僱信傳遞至被解僱的員工，加上公司要預留較充裕時間讓被解僱的員工執拾個人物品，即日內離開公司，所以10時05分是員工被解僱的「黃金時間」了。如果你或身邊同事被解僱，不妨留意時間吧。"},{"pid":"36d809dc95511a551b984a545e38617da0319594","tid":2360573,"uid":107681,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"解僱信唔係hr出要大老闆親自出，親力親為好老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513ef5570a425096dd94d586b7fce36a8cee2338","tid":2360573,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T02:12:14.000Z","msg":"由於高層或老闆通常會稍晚一點回到公司，他們上班時隨即會把解僱信傳至人事部，此時已是10時左右。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHR要炒你都唔會即日先知同出解僱信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />HR唔洗預備文件咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618d8a703451245197a6d424e77900eef8b988be","tid":2360573,"uid":373119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T02:15:50.000Z","msg":"每日都遲到 10 點半先返 就可以避開炒魷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9594d664e8ebe2cc5fe9bec398574bd12635e9","tid":2360573,"uid":33566,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T02:17:12.000Z","msg":"On9真係炒既前一晚access card email login system login坐部ban哂<br />\n你檯底部電腦都會搬走埋，檯頭direct line會route返去你大佬到<br />\n第二日朝早HR係門口等你，直接帶你入會議室<br />\n做完文件搵人望住你返個位執野再送你落樓下<br />\n寫呢篇文果個係咪仲讀緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752257d2583d4c4702551746f19f33b84552cc22","tid":2360573,"uid":55386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T02:19:45.000Z","msg":"我番親果D公司 都係臨收工先炒人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6af540c0ccf8845173ecefac20700fd15044d4","tid":2360573,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fe8103faa1a410ee7624782ff43a7ae54d8d93","tid":2360573,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"早D炒好過啦,好過要你做到4點臨收工先俾信你,last day都俾佢用到盡."},{"pid":"ee0ab7b5d61af1c74dced1a857a58757ae33895a","tid":2360573,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T02:05:37.000Z","msg":"趁10點05分推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268c9f9aeb89695ee4a750f57a6d7877d950c809","tid":2360573,"uid":53027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T03:02:48.000Z","msg":"我公司通常等你做到17:00先比信"}]}